Fender Deluxe Nashville Tele Solidbody Electric Guitar - Daphne Blue The Fender Deluxe Nashville Telecaster solidbody electric guitar delivers classic Tele playability, plus expanded sonic options thanks to its 3-pickup configuration and 5-way switching. At the bridge and neck positions, you'll find Fender's Vintage Noiseless Tele single-coil pickups, delivering vintage Tele tone without the vintage hum. And with a Vintage Noiseless Strat pickup in between, you've got way more sonic versatility than with a 2-pickup Tele. Ebay's FedEx calculator on the item page quotes eBay's discounted FedEx shipping rates, which we honor. At checkout, however, buyers in certain areas will see the calculator attempt to charge the full retail price. FedEx's full retail price is the price you pay if you were to walk into a FedEx retail location. The difference between eBay's discounted rate and this retail price can be as much as 40%. If you estimate shipping with a zip code that is different from the zip code registered to your User ID, eBay’s shipping calculator will make the adjustment at checkout. FedEx does this based on the +4 extension of your primary 5-digit zip code. For example, eBay’s shipping calculator may quote you one price based on your primary 5-digit zip, and then figure out that your requested street address at checkout places you within the rural surcharge area, changing the shipping price to an alternate amount that was originally quoted. If there is a discrepancy in your shipping cost, please send us a screen shot of the quoted price to you on our item page and we can override the eBay checkout calculation to get you the cheapest rate.
